title: Code of the West 2012
description:
A fine documentary regarding cannabis policy in the state of Montana, USA.

Politically, I guess there's very little reason to release outside the States, and that is probably part of the reason why they didn't. It is available for streaming free in a bunch of places, but region locked. 

This is a Hulu rip for the benefit of non-US residents.
